# ==========================================
# 通用多项目 SpringBoot 全局忽略规则
# ==========================================

# --- 基础说明文件 (可选，如果不希望上传根目录以外的 HELP.md) ---
**/HELP.md

# --- 编译产物 (匹配任何目录下的 target 文件夹) ---
target/
**/target/
build/
**/build/
bin/
out/

# --- Maven/Gradle 依赖与封装 ---
.mvn/
**/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
**/wrapper/maven-wrapper.properties
.gradle/
**/build.log

# --- 例外规则：确保 src 目录下的特定 target 不被误杀 (通常保持默认即可) ---
!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/

# --- STS (Eclipse) 相关 ---
.apt_generated
.classpath
.factorypath
.project
.settings/
.springBeans
.sts4-cache

# --- IntelliJ IDEA 相关 (全局匹配所有子项目的配置) ---
.idea/
**/.idea/
*.iws
*.iml
*.ipr
**/out/

# --- NetBeans 相关 ---
**/nbproject/private/
**/nbbuild/
**/dist/
**/nbdist/
**/.nb-gradle/

# --- VS Code 相关 ---
.vscode/
**/.vscode/

# --- 操作系统与日志 ---
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db